>> title: Gin Sour
>> glass: coupe
>> technique: shake
>> tags: gin,shaken,lemon

Chill a #coupe{} in the freezer.

Fill a #cocktail shaker{} with @ice{}.

Pour @lemon juice{1%oz} over a barspoon of @sugar{1%tsp} into shaker. Add @gin{2%oz} and @bitters{3%shakes}.

Shake at least 30 seconds. Serve in chilled coupe.